Vansant Sandbox
A standalone Electron + React + Monaco desktop workspace for building projects planned in VansantPlatform.
Features in v1
Open folder
File explorer
Open files in tabs
Edit and save files
Create files and folders
Monaco editor
Run Python, JavaScript, TypeScript, and Java files
Output panel
Install
npm install
Run in dev
npm run dev
Build
npm run dist:win
Notes
Python must be available as `python` on PATH.
Node must be available for JS/TS run actions.
TypeScript run uses `npx tsx`.
Java run expects `javac` and `java` on PATH.